{"tid":935372,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[又抄]厚顏無恥既中國香港人經營之道","createTime":"2018-12-10T03:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T05:07:26.000Z","uid":196751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"083cfc1ccff445adbcd969ca0e845fc96cb9a02c","tid":935372,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"猶太人同中國人點做生意大家都知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GLaBkCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGLaBkCQ.jpg&h=3cba72ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗有檔食肉骨茶<br />\n利申左先,間野長期都好撚多人排隊,根本唔需要請打手<br />\n我開呢個post只係見到間翻版真係幾肉酸先講下,所以名都唔開<br />\n<br />\n咁呢個週末發現正版果間既後一條街有間差唔多樣既野<br />\n只係改左名,但係一模一樣既鋪<br />\n係一樣到連裝修門面,餐牌都一撚樣,連個名都學人叫xy‧xy<br />\n我就屎忽痕走去問下正版既係咪有分店,正版話只此一間,<br />\n最後我都有入呢間老翻試下,真係除左員工個樣同鋪頭名唔同,其他都抄到足...<br />\n唉....香港應該唔洗幾耐會好似大陸咁,連kfc,m記都夠膽老翻<br />\n<br />\n頭盔:圖文唔一定相符<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TEhPFCR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTEhPFCR.jpg&h=fee3a9aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07822d60332ae63ecbce8cc8c3bd07eeaefe07de","tid":935372,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01144403178fcbb89ee520a18dc9cbb904123791","tid":935372,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58009ffb1cd927124c5087408f2afa0160f645a","tid":935372,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22ebdd280be7ce51358e6bfdaa5a8223d5e70ea","tid":935372,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦 好出奇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那香港係咁<i